# Trivy suppressions. Every entry is a known, reviewed, accepted finding — kept here
# (not muted silently) so the reasoning is visible and re-checkable. Only add an ID
# after understanding why it does not apply.

# --- Legacy GCP asset bucket (deploy/iac/gcp) ---
# The GCP stack is being decommissioned for Cloudflare Pages. These three MEDIUM
# misconfigs originate in Google's own cloud-foundation-fabric module and are
# intentional for a public-read static-asset bucket. They disappear when the GCP
# stack is torn down. Re-review (and likely delete this block) at that point.
AVD-GCP-0002
AVD-GCP-0077
AVD-GCP-0078

# --- lightningcss (MPL-2.0) ---
# A build-time CSS transformer pulled in by Tailwind v4 / Vite. It runs during the
# build and is NOT distributed in web/dist. MPL-2.0 is a file-level reciprocal
# license whose obligations trigger only on modifying and distributing the MPL
# files themselves, which we do not do. Safe to use as a dependency.
MPL-2.0
